Package: voe
Title: Vibration of Effects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chirag J.", "Patel", email = "chirag@hms.harvard.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8756-8525"))
Description: Estimate the distribution of effect sizes and p-values due to
    model specification choices. Given a base exposure-outcome model, VoE
    systematically fits all (or a random sample of) possible covariate
    adjustment subsets and visualizes the resulting variability in estimates
    and statistical significance.
